---

### 🌐 3. Create a GitHub Repo

1. Go to: [https://github.com/new](https://github.com/new)
2. **Repo name**: `StatementReconciliationTool`
3. Leave everything blank (don’t init with README)
4. Click **Create repository**

---

### 🧑‍💻 4. Upload via Git

Open a terminal in your folder and run:

```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Streamlit reconciliation tool"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/StatementReconciliationTool.git
git push -u origin main